Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.08,0:10:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,請進
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.71,0:10:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,情況怎樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.09,0:10:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,咲太
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.30,0:10:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你來了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.05,0:10:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,今天我把雙葉也帶來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.17,0:10:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.51,0:10:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.05,0:10:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我們說來就來 不妨礙吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.55,0:10:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.43,0:10:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,完全沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.06,0:10:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我好開心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.22,0:10:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.68,0:10:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你剛才在學習嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.44,0:10:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.69,0:10:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,正好 有些事能問問兩位嗎?
